---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Resonant Pioneer NFT - ResonantOS" description="The Resonant Pioneer NFT is a capped non-transferable early-adopter credential for the first 1000 eligible ResonantDAO Community Members.">
	<section class="px-4 pb-16 pt-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
			<p class="mb-5 font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-400">Pioneer</p>
			<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-6xl">The first 1000 early adopters.</h1>
			<p class="mt-8 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-8 text-zinc-300">
				The Resonant Pioneer NFT is a capped, non-transferable credential for early Community Members who help shape ResonantDAO while the foundation is still being built.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Hard Cap</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">Only 1000 Pioneer credentials can be issued by the membership program.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Membership Required</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">A wallet must have active Community Member status before it can receive the Pioneer credential.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Soulbound</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">Pioneer status belongs to the wallet that earned it. It cannot be sold or transferred.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl rounded-lg border border-emerald-400/20 bg-emerald-400/[0.06] p-6">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Open Design Point</h2>
			<p class="mt-4 text-zinc-300">
				The DAO still needs to decide whether Pioneer means the first 1000 Community Members or the first 1000 Community Members who complete an additional early-adopter action.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
